{
  "id": "adv_card_ktn_07_03",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃 3話 沢山の収穫",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――映画撮影のクランクアップからしばらくした頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Sometime after the movie finished filming",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 0.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "この衣装を着るのが、久しぶりな気がします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It feels like it’s been a while since I last wore this outfit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.466666611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.366666611
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "すっかり着こなすようになったな、よく似合ってるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve really grown into it. It suits you well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.366666611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.7335373958
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "今日の宣伝ポスターの撮影とコメント撮りが終わったら\nこのお仕事もひと段落か……なんだか寂しいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Once we finish shooting the promotional posters and comments today‚\nthis job will be done… I’m a little sad‚  actually.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.3668708325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "寂しさもあるけど……俺はとにかく\n無事に終えられて良かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m a little sad too‚  but… Above all‚  I’m\nglad that we finished it without a hitch.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――映画の撮影直前のこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Just before the movie shoot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.5461902698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 28.8795237065
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃……よくここまで演技が上達したな\n一体どうやったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono… You’ve really improved your acting.\nHow did you do it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "紹介してもらったコーチに、演技の基礎を\n叩き込んでもらったおかげでもあるんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The coach you introduced me to drilled the basics\nof acting into me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.7088432472,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "葵さんと一緒に過ごした時間の影響が\n一番大きいのかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think the time I spent with Aoi-san\nhad the biggest impact.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.2704483234,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "葵と一緒に……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With Aoi…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.7755090476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "全体的な演技は、練習のたびに\n上達してる手応えがあったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I could feel myself improving with every practice‚\nin general.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.4516114236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、親友と再会する一番重要なシーンで\nどんな感情を乗せたらいいか掴み切れなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I couldn’t quite grasp what kind of emotions\nto put into it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.9182780903,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "そうしたら葵さんに――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then Aoi-san――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.118277224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "「二人仲良く過ごせば、親友が敵として\n現れた時の辛さも分かるんじゃない？」って提案されて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Maybe if we spend time together as friends‚\nyou’ll understand how painful it would be to see her as an enemy?”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.0849447569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "それから、プライベートはなるべく葵さんと一緒に\n過ごすようにしてみたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so I tried to spend as much time with Aoi-san as I could‚\neven in my private time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.2516114236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "初めはどうなるかと思ったんですけど……\n自然と、前より距離が縮まった気がして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was worried about how it would go at first‚  but…\nI feel like we naturally grew closer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.3849437397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "おかげで、親友と対峙した時のショックと、それでも\n救ってみせるという強い意志を持つ感覚が掴めたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to that‚  I was able to understand the shock of confronting my best friend‚\nand my strong will to save her despite it all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.518277073,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどな……葵と二人で役作りをした訳か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… So you worked on your character with Aoi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.4516095401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、それが原因で渚が拗ねちゃって\n機嫌を直してもらうのが大変でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But that ended up making Nagisa sulk‚\nand it was really hard to cheer her up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.0133790335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "後は、莉央さんがパンケーキを食べようと\n葵さんを誘ったんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then Rio-san invited Aoi-san\nto go eat pancakes…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.0800457002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "「これから琴乃とデートだから」って断って\n莉央さんがシュンとしちゃったこともありました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but she turned her down‚  saying “I’m going on a date with Kotono.”\nThat made Rio-san really depressed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.213382594,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あちこちに影響は出てたんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like there were a lot of repercussions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.2133817277,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "最初は凄く焦りましたけど……今度こそ大丈夫です\n撮影、楽しみにしていて下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was really flustered at first‚  but… I’ll be fine this time.\nPlease look forward to the shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.1102760953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.1769427619
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.1769427619
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "沢山悩んだ分、今の自分が出来る精一杯の\n演技が出来たと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think I was able to give the best performance I could‚\nafter all the worrying I did.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.1102760953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.0769322318
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "あ……スタッフさんに呼ばれました\nそれじゃあ、行ってきますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… The staff is calling me.\nI’ll be back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.0769427619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.5102655651
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "今日最後の仕事だ、頑張ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is your last job for the day‚  good luck.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.5102655651,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "はい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.6015127899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_03-ktn019.m4a",
      "text": "このバイクの前で映画のセリフを披露……ですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have to deliver a line from the movie in front of this motorcycle…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.001505669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
